-- Ghana names Barclays, StanChart and Deutsche Bank as Eurobond advisors
-- 
-- Fri May 30, 2014 06:02AM EDT
-- None



ACCRA, May 30 (Reuters) - Ghana named Barclays Plc <BARC.L>, Deutsche Bank <DBKGn.DE> and Standard Chartered Plc <STAN.L> as transaction advisers for its 2014 Eurobond of up to $1.5 billion, the finance ministry said on Friday.

